          <physDesc>
            <objectDesc>
              <supportDesc material="parchment">
                <support>
                  <p>Fol. <ref target="https://corpuscoranicum.de/de/verse-navigator/sura/27/verse/19/manuscripts/1944/page/1r">1 recto</ref> is hair side, fol. <ref target="https://corpuscoranicum.de/de/verse-navigator/sura/27/verse/14/manuscripts/1944/page/1v">1 verso</ref> is flesh side. </p>
                  <p>Text division: Simple verse separator consists of a group of three strokes arranged one  above the other in the shape of an arrow. Tenth verse separator is  illuminated with gold, red and brown ink.  </p>
                </support>
                <extent>Folios: 1
